title: Supremacy
lyrics:
[Instrumental Intro]
[Verse]
Wake to see, your true emancipation is a fantasy
Policies have risen up and overcome the brave
Greatness dies, unsung and lost, invisible to history
Embedded spies brainwashing our children to be mean
[Chorus]
You don't have long
I am on to you
The time, it has come to destroy...
Your supremacy
[Guitar Solo]
[Interlude]
Oh-ooh-oh-oh
Oh-ooh-oh-oh
[Chorus]
You don't have long
I am on to you
The time, it has come to destroy...
Your supremacy

[Instrumental Bridge]
[Outro]
Supremacy
Yeah, ooh, yeah-yeah-ooh
